metadata.name: Fabrik Society™ Red
metadata.description:
Fabrik Society™ Red offers artists an affordable way to submit their works for consideration by Fabrik Society's esteemed curators, and receive opportunities to exhibit their art at events such as The LA Art Show, Art Palm Beach, Photo Independent Milan, Context Art Miami, Val Kilmer’s Kamp Kilmer, The Duchess Gallery, the Official Gallery of The Duchess of York and more. Priced at just $29.99, this membership is the most accessible way for artists to gain exposure, network with industry professionals, and take their careers to the next level.

The collective is continually adding exhibitions, both in-person physical and digital, and virtual galleries, to provide its members with a wealth of opportunities to showcase their work. 

* Please be advised that as a Fabrik Society™ Red member, you are given the opportunity to submit your works for consideration. However, it does not guarantee that your works will be selected for exhibition by the curation team.

Join today and take your career to the next level.

Important: Please visit FabrikSociety.io for submission deadlines.
